CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, June 8, 1957, pg. A13 reads: "Magic Surrounds Girl Friends' Pittsburgh Meet"
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of twelve women, including one wearing dark lace scoop neck long sleeved dress with corsage, posed in Webster Hall with patterned carpet and landscape mural, for Thirtieth Anniversary Convention of Girl Friends, Inc.
